name: Joker Max XMD
desc: A versatile WhatsApp bot supporting multiple device connections, developed by Iconic Tech.
guide:
1. Clone the repository: git clone https://github.com/iconic05/Joker-Max-XMD.git
2. Navigate to the project directory: cd Joker-Max-XMD
3. Install dependencies: npm install
4. Start the bot: npm start
